# GitHub Actions CI Readiness

Application: `{{ app.name }}`
Container image: `{{ image }}`

This directory contains generated GitHub Actions workflow files for a local DevSecOps lab.
The workflows are intentionally readable and conservative. `k8s-forge` does not push code, publish container images, deploy Kubernetes resources, or create GitHub secrets.

## Generated Workflows

{% if ci.python.enabled -%}
- `.github/workflows/ci.yml`: Python quality, tests, security audit, and package build.
{% endif -%}
{% if ci.container.enabled -%}
- `.github/workflows/security.yml`: local Docker image build, Trivy image scan, Syft SBOM generation, and report artifact upload.
{% endif %}

If this directory was generated outside `.github/workflows/`, review the files first, then copy the workflow files into your repository `.github/workflows/` directory.

